Project Title: Personal Blog Web App

Overview:

This is a full-stack blog application where users can create, edit, and delete blog posts. The project focuses on content management with a clean UI and user-friendly experience. It serves as a basic CMS (Content Management System) built with Python and Django.


---

Key Features:

Create / Edit / Delete Blog Posts
Users can add new articles, modify existing ones, or delete them entirely.

Post Listing and Detail View
Homepage displays all blog posts with titles, summaries, and timestamps. Clicking on a post shows the full content.

Django Admin Integration
Admin panel to manage all posts easily.

Responsive UI
Clean, minimal, and mobile-friendly layout.



---

Tech Stack:

Backend: Django (Python)

Frontend: HTML, CSS, Django Templating

Database: SQLite (default Django DB)

Other Tools: Git, GitHub
